In this line of work, we developed a novel theoretical, methodological, and statistical framework based in large part on [Craik's (2009) Network Interpretation of Reputations](https://books.google.com/books?id=H9oBQSUm7gkC&dq=Reputation:+A+network+interpretation&lr=&source=gbs_navlinks_s) and [Dave Kenny's (1994) Interpersonal Perception](https://psycnet.apa.org/record/1994-98901-000)